quest.achieve_cond_description: Raise any character from the FINAL FANTASY VII realm to level 10 or higher.
quest.description:
Raise a character from FINAL FANTASY VII to level 10!
Cloud is a character from the FINAL FANTASY VII realm who can be recruited by completing the Mako Reactor No. 5 (VII) dungeon .
When fighting in dungeons from their native realm, characters get a Record Synergy bonus.
The Record Synergy bonus boosts characters' stats and the EXP they earn.
Recruit characters from each realm to have the perfect party ready at a moment's notice!
quest.title: Level 10 Character (FINAL FANTASY VII)
